      "file_path": "feature-eelf/src/main/feature/config/logback-eelf.xml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 32,
      "message": "Do you really want %mdc here?   I think this will output all the MDC fields, so the would be a lot of duplication with the other %X fields.\n\nGeneral comment.",
